TopicTitle: Mods only downloading a handful of parts

Articles.Content: I have recently tried to get back into KSP after switching computers to find it seems most mods only download a fraction of the parts it should download. I have searched everywhere on the internet but found nothing like what I am experiencing. I am running 32x and tryng to download B9 aerospace, which only gives me 82 parts and OPT space planes which gives me ten. I also have BD armory but it isn't missing any parts. Help...? ![:confused:](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif)
